txt.en: Food can be found in Fushaum Bal North.\n\nYou should steal food from Fushaum Bal North while avoiding the guards.
<rgb=#FF0000>Don't let the Fushaum Guards spot you</rgb>
A guard spotted you sneaking around!
Thâng can be found at Fushaum Bal South.\n\nYou should talk to Thâng.
'Ah this food will continue sustaining us for quite some time!'
The encampment of Fushaum Bal is a lawless home to evil men once under the command of Sauron.
Fushaum Bal South: Dealing in Stealing
Steal food from Fushaum Bal North ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

Now that the road to Nurn is blocked, our food supply is running low.

'Khirgi has sent men to hunt sûlokil, but has plenty of meats. Steal some of his provisions for us.'

<rgb=#FF0000>Note: This quest is only available while the quest, The Fushaum Resolution, is underway.</rgb>
